msgstr "赋予年轻人智慧"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_striped_center_top
msgid ""
"Empower young minds with quality education and engaging learning experiences "
"that nurture creativity, play, and academic excellence."
msgstr ""
"通过优质教育和引人入胜的学习体验，培养创造力、游戏精神和卓越的学业成绩，增强"
"青少年的思维能力。"

